<div class="column">
	<h2>SQL Server database backup</h2>
	<p class="text">Iperius Backup is a lightweight and easy-to-configure software to backup Microsoft SQL Server database. It allows in a few simple steps to make backups of SQL Server 2005, SQL Server 2008, 2012, SQL Server 2014, SQL Server 2016 and SQL Server 2017, and to run the restore automatically. Iperius can also make backups of the free database SQL Server Express Edition, and back up remote databases.</p>
</div>
<div class="clearfix">
</div>
<div class="column" style="padding-top:50px; text-align:center;">
<a target="_blank" class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary pmd-z-depth"  href="http://www.iperiusbackup.net/en/sql-server-backup-iperius/"><i style="font-size:11pt;" class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;Read the tutorial</a>     
</div>


<div class="separator">
	<div class="separatorShadow">
	</div>
</div>
<br />
<div class="column medium">
	<h2>Database backup to FTP, Cloud, Tape, NAS</h2>
	<p class="text">Iperius allows to make several integrated backups at the same time: you can back up a SQL Server database and immediately send it via FTP to another server, or to cloud storage services like Google Drive / OneDrive / Dropbox. For maximum security and transfer speed, Iperius can use the FTPS protocol and automatically make the zip compression and encryption of backup files.</p>
</div>
<div class="column medium last">
	<h2>Low cost even on server systems</h2>
	<p class="text">Iperius Backup is the most convenient software to make backups of local or remote SQL Server database, since in one comprehensive solution you have a great number of built-in features, and there are no limitations in the number of databases or additional costs for server systems. You can run unlimited backup operations, also in parallel mode.</p>
</div>
                          
<div class="clearfix">
</div>

<div class="column medium">
	<h2>Compression, verification, e-mail notifications</h2>
	<p class="text">Iperius Backup adds many important features to the database backup. It 's possible to run the native compression and the zip compression of backup files, enable the advanced backup verification, and the AES encryption to protect confidential data. Iperius also allows to set up automated backups and keep multiple backup copies. Finally, you have detailed email notification functions to always stay informed about the result of your backups.</p>
</div>
<div class="column medium last">
	<h2>Compatible with all SQL Server editions</h2>
	<p class="text">Iperius Backup is compatible with all editions of Microsoft SQL Server database: from the older versions (2005) up to the latest SQL Server 2008, 2012, SQL Server 2014, SQL Server 2016, SQL Server 2017. Iperius Backup can also make backups of SQL Express, the free version of the Microsoft database.</p>
</div>
